COMPREHENSIVE DATABASE CLEANUP & ALIGNMENT
One Document. Complete System. Clean Architecture.

üìã OVERVIEW
What This Does:

Drops 40+ legacy tables (collections, curations, prompts, letterbox, etc.)
Cleans up 50+ unused functions
Renames for clarity: notebooks ‚Üí folders ‚Üí sections ‚Üí pages
Uses JSONB operators (no JSONPath)
Implements mail-inline-in-today flow
Complete transclusion model (template ‚Üí clone ‚Üí snapshot)
Publishing, replay, everything

Hierarchy:
User
