**Server-Side Handler (PHP/Node/Python):**
```php
// /api/sections/submit.php

if ($_SERVER['REQUEST_METHOD'] !== 'POST') {
  header('HTTP/1.1 405 Method Not Allowed');
  exit('Method Not Allowed');
}

$section_id = $_POST['section_id'] ?? null;
$include_replay = $_POST['include_replay'] === 'true';

if (!$section_id) {
  header('HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request');
  exit('Missing section_id');
}

// Call Supabase RPC
$result = $supabase->rpc('create_submission_snapshot', [
  'p_section_id' => $section_id,
  'p_user_id' => $user_id,
  'p_include_replay' => $include_replay
]);

// Redirect to gallery
header('Location: /groups/' . $group_id . '/gallery');
exit();
```

**Progressive Enhancement (JavaScript Optional):**
```javascript
// Enhance form with AJAX (optional)
document.querySelector('.submission-form')
  ?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();

    const formData = new FormData(e.target);

    try {
      const response = await fetch(e.target.action, {
        method: 'POST',
        body: formData
      });

      if (response.ok) {
        // Optimistic UI update
        showToast('Tear-out created!');
        // Let server redirect handle navigation
        window.location.href = response.url;
      }
    } catch (error) {
      // Fallback: let form submit normally
      e.target.submit();
    }
  });
```

