## What Is Cursive? (30-Second Version)

**The problem:**
- Everything online is algorithmic feeds or AI slop
- No infrastructure for human curation at scale
- Digital tools pull you away from physical world

**The solution:**
Cursive is **protocol for curated human experiences**.

- **Hosts** create series of invitations (not assignments)
- **Guests** respond with craft (writing, drawing, photos)
- **AI** connects but never creates (sidebar suggestions, never inline)
- **Location** matters (GPS-locked prompts, nature ID, local boards)
- **Provenance** preserved (replay shows process, version history)

