## Common Pitfalls

### ‚ùå Don't: AI writes inline

```tsx
// BAD
<Editor>
  {aiGeneratedText}  {/* Never! */}
</Editor>
```

### ‚úÖ Do: AI suggests in sidebar

```tsx
// GOOD
<div>
  <Editor />
  <ThinkingSidebar />  {/* Suggestions here */}
</div>
```

---

### ‚ùå Don't: Track user behavior

```sql
-- BAD
CREATE TABLE user_activity (
  user_id UUID,
  action TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);
```

### ‚úÖ Do: Show work, not behavior

```sql
-- GOOD
CREATE TABLE snapshots (
  section_id UUID,
  payload JSONB  -- The work itself
);
```

---

### ‚ùå Don't: Use jargon in UI

```tsx
// BAD
<button>Fork submission to workspace</button>
```

### ‚úÖ Do: Use physical metaphors

```tsx
// GOOD
<button>Make tear-out</button>
```

---

### ‚ùå Don't: Track location continuously

```tsx
// BAD
useEffect(() => {
  setInterval(() => {
    trackUserLocation();
  }, 60000);
}, []);
```

### ‚úÖ Do: Check only when user initiates

```tsx
// GOOD
<button onClick={checkLocation}>
  Unlock prompt
</button>
```

